Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
i think a coin has two sides. it is difficult to say whether living in campus dorm is good or bad. for some people, they may feel life is ease and comfortable while live on campus. you don't need drive for class. you just go to dining room for a meal. but some others prefer more private space, they choose to live off campus.